# 🎬 Ultra Downloader Pro

**Ultra Downloader Pro** is a full-stack web application that allows users to **download high-quality videos and audio** from platforms like **YouTube, Instagram, and Facebook** using secure cookie-based authentication.

> ⚡ Powered by Flask & yt-dlp • Deployable on [Render](https://render.com) • Clean UI • Fast performance

---

## 🔗 Live Demo

👉 *Coming soon on Render*  
🛠️ Deploy it yourself with 1-click on [Render](https://render.com)

---

## ✨ Features

- ✅ Supports downloads from **YouTube**, **Instagram**, and **Facebook**
- 🔐 **Cookie-based login** for private/restricted content
- 🎵 Download in **MP4 / MP3 / best available formats**
- 🚀 Multithreaded download support
- 📊 Live progress display during downloads
- 🧹 Auto-delete files after download completes
- 💻 Simple, responsive & dark-themed frontend UI
- 📂 Deploy-ready with `render.yaml` config

---

## 🧰 Tech Stack

| Technology     | Usage                         |
|----------------|-------------------------------|
| Python (Flask) | Web backend server            |
| yt-dlp         | Core video/audio downloader   |
| HTML/CSS/JS    | Frontend interface            |
| Render         | Cloud deployment              |

---

## 🏗 Project Structure




video-downloader/
│
├── static/ # Static files (CSS, images)
├── templates/ # HTML templates
├── cookies_instagram.txt # IG cookies (optional)
├── cookies_facebook.txt # FB cookies (optional)
├── cookies_youtube.txt # YT cookies (optional)
├── app.py # Main Flask application
├── requirements.txt # Python dependencies
├── render.yaml # Render deployment config
└── README.md




---

## 🚀 Run Locally

```bash
# Clone the repo
git clone https://github.com/rajsonugupta11/video-downloader.git
cd video-downloader

# Optional: Create virtual environment
python -m venv venv
venv\Scripts\activate  # On Windows

# Install required packages
pip install -r requirements.txt

# Start the Flask app
python app.py




🔐 Private Video Download (Cookies Setup)
To download content from private/follower-only accounts (Instagram, Facebook, YouTube):

Install this Chrome extension: Get cookies.txt

Log into your account (IG/FB/YT) in Chrome

Export cookies to a file

Save it as:

cookies_instagram.txt

cookies_facebook.txt

cookies_youtube.txt

Place those files in the root folder

📝 The app will automatically use these cookies during download.

